data.description: ***Seller offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs*** Enjoy the peaceful sounds of nature. Nestled on +/-5.77 wooded acres, this 3BR/2BA contemporary country home is a serene retreat with a natural spring, creek, and abundant wildlife. The layout includes a spacious office, galley-style kitchen, formal dining, and a family room with large windows opening to a deck with forest views. Additional features include a barn, workshop, chicken coop, and well water. Only 10 minutes from downtown Rogers and Prairie Creek Marina at Beaver Lake, 5 minutes to the Hwy 12 boat ramp. This property seamlessly blends country living with convenience. Perfect for a weekend retreat or a permanent escape, offering endless possibilities for a lakeside country lifestyle.
